<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>API: Image Search Abstraction Layer</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>API: Image Search Abstraction Layer</h1>
        <h4>User stories:</h4>
        <ol>
            <li>I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.</li>
            <li>I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.</li>
            <li>I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Example usage:</h2>
        <p><a href="<%= site %>/api/imagesearch/grumpy cat" target="_blank"><%= site %>/api/imagesearch/grumpy cat</a></p>
        <p><a href="<%= site %>/api/imagesearch/grumpy cat?offset=5" target="_blank"><%= site %>/api/imagesearch/grumpy cat?offset=5</a></p>
        <p><a href="<%= site %>/api/latest/imagesearch/" target="_blank"><%= site %>/api/latest/imagesearch/</a></p>

    </div>

</body>
</html>